spanGrp.span: Me, I was born in Ng'onyomba
The day arrived when we scattered
buneed qay gidatard qay aa motart gejeedo
What caused people to scatter was hunger
Kilichowatawanya watu si walitawanywa na njaa
Many who didn't go to Mang'ola...
su ga mawa mang'ola su gawa ng'wakal
Many who didn't go to Mang'ola went to Ng'wagara
People were hurting because of hunger
Watu waliumia kwa sababu ya njaa
ases qay gwalanyand qay qamew fugas hes qay gamewaj aa ases gad ewas manang'
We in the old days, an elder passed away and our elders passed away, when we were small
Sisi zamani mzee alifariki na wazee wetu walifariki sisi tukiwa wadogo
storyajeeg gid qay sing'etiday gwach gijenyasan ed gwalanyand iidu aa mad eran
We would get the story from the elder, but we won't meet him
Stori tungekuta kwa mzee lakini hatukumkuta
In the old days, my father passed away early
storiyajeeg su aa mad enal su ba qamn gid qay ng'etaytan
These stories we don't know how they started
Stori hizi hatujui hizi za sasa zilivyoanza
When these children are born, now
gejiil emed suko mad ga qay
They are born, and other people aren't of the old days any more
Wamezaliwa watu wengine siyo wa zamani tena
A child doesn't know any more
You try to send them and they refuse
geequs andawiin lapiy aa gichagd aa qamas
Maybe if you have money and try to send them they will agree
Labda uwe na hela ukamtuma atakubali
That thing of the past is over
What was lost, I don't know
I don't know if it is a sin
Or if it is something that comes with the years
Or if it is how people have changed
All of this, we don't know
I confused me, I don't know
What could I say? Me and...
emeed anin buneed gid qay analdayd qay buneed gab
People in the old days, how I know it, people in the old days were...
Watu zamani mimi nilivyojua watu zamani walikuwa...
gab iit akalele qamn aa mad gab
They listened to each other, and now they don't
Now, how will I know what the reason for this is?
Sasa nitajua hili jambo sababu yake ni nini
ni ha saran ha digan ng'ul ni gije mpak aa ewu siyag
This, don't look at this until we become one person
Hili usilitazame mpaka tutakuwa mtu mmoja
qwaroot kabileed su manang'iin su gigagwaroodaj qawung nyeew madeb
It will get lost, these small tribes will lose their names
ltapotea kabila hizi ndogo zitapoteza majina yao
Even if it is from wherever, it won't be known any more
mad qwanalad geyet aa mad ebugd gid qay ba saman mandan
Thay have already forgotten each other and that won't return to the old ways, there's no way
